```

There are a few ways to capture the data.

I recommend dividing the text, using the _[String#indexOf](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/21/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/String.html#indexOf(int))_, or _[String#split](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/21/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/String.html#split(java.lang.String))_, method.

