  [2]: https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/wiki/Spring-Boot-2.0-Release-Notes#configuration-property-binding
  [3]: https://docs.spring.io/spring-framework/docs/5.0.x/javadoc-api/org/springframework/context/annotation/Bean.html
  [4]: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/53462889/create-n-number-of-beans-with-beandefinitionregistrypostprocessor
  [5]: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/48161636/spring-boot-dynamic-bean-creation-from-properties-file

